==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Spot stroke
<hw>Spot stroke</hw>. <fld>(Eng. Billiards)</fld> <def>The pocketing of
the red ball in a top corner pocket from off its own spot so as to leave
the cue ball in position for an easy winning hazard in either top corner
pocket.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Spotted</ent>⟦br⟧
